{"tid":421511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南丫海難5周年　生還者轟政府零交代","createTime":"2017-10-02T09:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T13:30:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"03ef288527a85a419b6f54d35513217835fe609f","tid":421511,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20170390&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20170390%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171002&d=dbPDPaYoj6NyKd01Z6DEHsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0e232a0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20170390%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171002&h=e4a635f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20170390&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171002</a><br />\n<br />\n南丫海難5周年　生還者轟政府零交代<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171002/large/02la3p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171002%2Flarge%2F02la3p7.jpg&h=3f07f9e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有團體昨在中環碼頭撒溪錢，悼念南丫海難死者。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】5年前南丫海難葬送39條生命，十．一變成「港殤」，政府以刑事、公務員紀律調查及私隱為由，至今仍未完全公開海難調查報告。今年更是特首林鄭月娥班子新上任，有生還者指政府過去一年並無交代調查進展。逾30名市民昨晚自發舉行悼念活動，悼念一眾死難者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民中環拜祭死者<br />\n<br />\n悼念活動於中環碼頭舉行，現場放置39個麵包，代表39名死難者，現場展示多張南丫海難相片。參與市民於海難發生時間晚上8時23分默哀5分鐘，然後將祭品燒掉，參與者逐一上香，隨即撒溪錢落海。<br />\n<br />\n悼念活動發起人之一的梁金成表示，南丫海難屬香港不幸，政府應發起悼念活動及取消十．一煙花匯演，他批評林鄭出席十．一酒會竟未有主動提及南丫海難，「係咪應該講幾句安撫香港人」。<br />\n<br />\n從事電燈工程的李先生表示首次出席悼念活動，認為海難死者死於不幸，又指船上的安全問題嚴重，批評海事處辦事不力。從事酒吧業的郭先生第二年參與悼念活動，認為市民應反思應否在這天觀賞煙花慶祝，並批評政府每年放煙花慶祝十．一，視39名海難死者如草芥，毫不尊重。<br />\n運輸及房屋局局長陳帆昨上任後首次回應南丫海難，指警方刑事調查仍在進行，不適宜過早評論會否公開報告，又指願與家屬會面。<br />\n<br />\n不過，海難生還者趙炳全接受傳媒訪問時指，若政府官員會面沒有實質內容，只想講安慰說話，則毋須約見。他認為有刑事調查不等於報告所有內容都不可以公開，又指政府過去一年已經沒再與他們聯絡交代調查進展。「你哋（政府）做咗啲乜嘢，或者對呢批海事處人員嘅懲處方向係點樣，呢幾年我哋唔知道政府做過啲乜嘢，還是係冇做過嘢，由得時間就咁流走。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者張文鈴、謝明明"},{"pid":"e6b3b4ed0f51876e07d365d5663251cae950bf2f","tid":421511,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7d582da12a96851f879a52f3b074e8d44c3330","tid":421511,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"一年容易又中秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154d5eb373a6cd18772af3be29e879fc071fc6ae","tid":421511,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aa02bbeb10ac0a06f6d3052807e62cd7cf228cd","tid":421511,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"仲夠擔放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4637bc84a5f512d27accfeb437262a5f22ecf4da","tid":421511,"uid":76776,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"585d1431bd84f330287602a4ab2cdc67be5c466e","tid":421511,"uid":14625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/193221_5d5eafd90bd7ef90b77820ca0194e5e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F193221_5d5eafd90bd7ef90b77820ca0194e5e0.jpg&h=460a49b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42cca54d8b3a10712e008698beac5a26ed7e354","tid":421511,"uid":22095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"5年都未查完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/